com.anji.fingerprint
Class Classification

java.lang.Object
  com.anji.fingerprint.Classification
public class Classification
extends java.lang.Object

Enumerated type representing fingerprint classifications: whorl, right loop, left loop, arch, and tented arch. Values returned in toString() are single-character representations of classification.

Author:
Philip Tucker
